mixin onboarding(step)
  case step
    
    when 1
      p
        | Entering this data will allow Spyre to track your progress over time.
      p Â 
        form
          .input-group
            .input-row
              label Cigarettes smoked per day
              input(type='text', placeholder='')
            .input-row
              label Cost per pack
              input(type='text', placeholder='')
            .input-row
              label Date Quit
              input(type='date', placeholder='')
        a.button-main(href='/onboarding/2', data-transition='slide-in') next
    
    when 2
      p When you go on vacation, do you&hellip;
        a.button-main(href='/onboarding/3', data-transition='slide-in') have a plan
        |  or 
        a.button-main(href='/onboarding/3', data-transition='slide-in') wing it

    when 3
      p in school, do you like
        a.button-main(href='/onboarding/4', data-transition='slide-in') science class
        |  or 
        a.button-main(href='/onboarding/4', data-transition='slide-in') art class

    when 4
      p In general, do you&hellip;
        a.button-main(href='/onboarding/5', data-transition='slide-in') seek truth
        |  or
        a.button-main(href='/onboarding/5', data-transition='slide-in') empathize with others

    when 5
      p How long after you wake up do you have your first cigarette?
        input(type='text', placeholder='')
        a.button-main(href='/home', data-transition='slide-in') done